PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Albert A. Vincent, of Saint John, New Brunswick, as a director of the board of directors of the Saint John Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of David Ross MacPherson, whose term has expired.
